&lt;/div>&lt;p>I did not understand what happened so I decided to google it! The &lt;a href="https://www.mail-archive.com/search?l=debian-bugs-dist@lists.debian.org&amp;amp;q=subject:%22Bug%23913982%5C%3A+r%5C-base%5C-core%5C%3A+R+executable+wrapper+scripts+hard%5C-code+the+wrong+path+to+sed.%22&amp;amp;o=newest&amp;amp;f=1">bug was already identified and reported &amp;#x1f604;&lt;/a>. A side note to mention that several packages now imports
